{"tid":2152379,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"間諜首選！中國成功研發使用蛋白質來儲存數據，可以植入人體。","createTime":"2020-08-12T03:02:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T03:06:42.000Z","uid":48040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4dfbfc53cb34c4fdfb9fc3d30dcbc90d4c0c4cee","tid":2152379,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T03:02:36.000Z","msg":"未來存儲硬盤可能不是半導體產品，而是來自蠶繭！中國科研人員研發出全球首款天然生物蛋白硬碟存儲器，「蠶絲硬碟」除了能儲存資料，還能裝入比如血液樣本、DNA等有機分子，甚至還可以植入人體。<br />\n<br />\n據《澎湃新聞》報導，「蠶絲硬碟」作為一種高容量、高可靠性的新型存儲技術，能同時存儲數字資訊和生命資訊；蠶絲蛋白是一種厭水性材料，在一定奈米尺度下會形成防水、防氣的結構，可保護包覆在其中的蛋白質、DNA等有機分子，相容性良好，<span class=\"orange\">可以植入活的生物體</span>，長期甚至永久保存，像電影中士兵佩戴的銘牌一樣，製成永不丟失的生命銘牌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200812/1782679.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20200812%2F1782679.htm&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf2LrBTEyyW%2B%2F%2BTJtsqEcrWg%3D&h=7fe08d8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200812/1782679.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/EagleNews_HK/status/1293381237365645312?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEagleNews_HK%2Fstatus%2F1293381237365645312%3Fs%3D20&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf2LrBTEyyW%2B%2F%2BTJtsqEcrWg%3D&h=e8137da6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEagleNews_HK%2Fstatus%2F1293381237365645312%3Fs%3D20&h=de91cd50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/EagleNews_HK/status/1293381237365645312?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"f60bc2dd0737f939daaa1cdb4dfdc7a0bbd3f076","tid":2152379,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T03:06:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1vDvpbR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1vDvpbR.jpg&h=cf5b7e7d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}